{"tid":1438212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《認真討論》重點反擊 - 林鄭經濟民生論","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T19:01:27.000Z","uid":264626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2958803a48d2bd2239d7f88927c21b671cb52b7c","tid":1438212,"uid":264626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"大家都意識到林鄭開始 spin，話呢場運動已經變質，老屈港獨，不過唔成功。<br />\n<br />\n依家開始打經濟民生牌，好多淺黃同淺藍好易受影響，佢地唔會思考太多，見到好似有D道理就變軚。<br />\n<br />\n所以呢刻一定要即時反擊，唔係淺黃，淺藍同街坊既支持好易流失。<br />\n<br />\n諗左D point ，請大家討論，加多D有力理據再做文章<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79887f78cae017730d0bd92b7bb6d7ab9f229068","tid":1438212,"uid":264626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dddaec8b1a8a8ad10e230e5283bf6c3a3935146","tid":1438212,"uid":264626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b5285a5641814f229e0ef52e829641d12c191d","tid":1438212,"uid":264626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73563c52d1d220973ec780fa6525f071256d8a4","tid":1438212,"uid":264626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkg